io.janusproject.kernel.repository

Class ParticipantRepository<ADDRESS extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.janusproject.kernel.repository.ParticipantRepository<ADDRESS>
  • Type Parameters:
    ADDRESS - - the generic type representing the address of a participant in the related space. This type must remains small, less than M in memory and must be Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultipleAddressParticipantRepository, UniqueAddressParticipantRepository

    public abstract class ParticipantRepository<ADDRESS extends Serializable>
extends Object
    An abstract repository providing the basic support of storage a collection a participant's address and its related listener.
